<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>GlowStudio - Beauty Parlour Booking</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
}

body{

background:
linear-gradient(
rgba(0,0,0,.55),
rgba(0,0,0,.55)
),

url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521590832167-7bcbfaa6381f?w=1800");

background-size:cover;
background-position:center;
background-attachment:fixed;

color:white;
}

/* Navbar */

nav{

display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;

padding:20px 60px;

background:rgba(0,0,0,.25);

backdrop-filter:blur(10px);

position:sticky;
top:0;
}

.logo{

font-size:34px;
font-weight:bold;

color:#FFD1DC;
}

nav ul{

display:flex;
gap:30px;
list-style:none;
}

nav ul li{

cursor:pointer;
transition:.3s;
}

nav ul li:hover{

color:#FFD1DC;
}

.btn{

padding:12px 25px;

border:none;

border-radius:30px;

font-weight:bold;

cursor:pointer;

background:
linear-gradient(
45deg,
#FFB6C1,
#FFD1DC
);
}

/* Hero */

.hero{

height:90vh;

display:flex;
flex-direction:column;

justify-content:center;
align-items:center;

text-align:center;

padding:20px;
}

.hero h1{

font-size:80px;

margin-bottom:20px;

background:
linear-gradient(
90deg,
#ffffff,
#FFD1DC,
#ffffff
);

-webkit-background-clip:text;
-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
}

.hero p{

font-size:22px;

max-width:850px;

color:#ffe6ee;
}

/* Appointment Form */

.booking-box{

margin-top:35px;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(12px);

padding:25px;

border-radius:20px;
}

.booking-box input,
.booking-box select{

padding:12px;

margin:10px;

border:none;

border-radius:10px;

width:200px;
}

/* Stats */

.stats{

display:flex;

justify-content:center;

flex-wrap:wrap;

gap:25px;

padding:50px;
}

.stat-card{

width:220px;

padding:25px;

text-align:center;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(10px);

border-radius:20px;
}

.stat-card h2{

color:#FFD1DC;
}

/* Section Title */

.section-title{

text-align:center;

font-size:40px;

color:#FFD1DC;

margin:50px 0;
}

/* Service Cards */

.container{

display:flex;

justify-content:center;

flex-wrap:wrap;

gap:30px;

padding:20px 40px 60px;
}

.card{

width:300px;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(15px);

border-radius:20px;

overflow:hidden;

transition:.4s;
}

.card:hover{

transform:translateY(-10px);

box-shadow:
0 15px 35px rgba(255,182,193,.3);
}

.card img{

width:100%;
height:220px;

object-fit:cover;
}

.card-content{

padding:20px;
}

.card-content h3{

color:#FFD1DC;

margin-bottom:10px;
}

/* Reviews */

.reviews{

display:flex;
justify-content:center;
flex-wrap:wrap;
gap:20px;
padding:30px;
}

.review{

width:300px;

padding:20px;

background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);

backdrop-filter:blur(10px);

border-radius:15px;
}

/* Footer */

footer{

text-align:center;

padding:25px;

background:rgba(0,0,0,.4);
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<nav>

<div class="logo">💄 GlowStudio</div>

<ul>

<li>Home</li>
<li>Services</li>
<li>Stylists</li>
<li>Appointments</li>
<li>Contact</li>

</ul>

<button class="btn">Login</button>

</nav>

<section class="hero">

<h1>Beauty Begins Here</h1>

<p>

Book salon appointments instantly and enjoy
premium beauty and wellness services.

</p>

<div class="booking-box">

<input type="text"
placeholder="Your Name">

<select>

<option>Select Service</option>

<option>Hair Styling</option>
<option>Facial</option>
<option>Makeup</option>
<option>Spa Therapy</option>

</select>

<input type="date">

<input type="time">

<button class="btn">

Book Appointment

</button>

</div>

</section>

<div class="stats">

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>50+</h2>
<p>Beauty Experts</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>20K+</h2>
<p>Happy Clients</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>100+</h2>
<p>Services</p>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<h2>24/7</h2>
<p>Online Booking</p>
</div>

</div>

<h2 class="section-title">

Our Premium Services

</h2>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1562322140-8baeececf3df?w=900">

<div class="card-content">

<h3>💇 Hair Styling</h3>

<p>
Professional haircuts, styling and treatments.
</p>

</div>

</div>

<div class="card">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1515377905703-c4788e51af15?w=900">

<div class="card-content">

<h3>✨ Facial Care</h3>

<p>
Luxury facials for glowing and healthy skin.
</p>

</div>

</div>

<div class="card">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522335789203-aabd1fc54bc9?w=900">

<div class="card-content">

<h3>💄 Bridal Makeup</h3>

<p>
Elegant makeup services for special occasions.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

<h2 class="section-title">

Customer Reviews

</h2>

<div class="reviews">

<div class="review">
⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐<br><br>
Amazing service and very professional staff.
</div>

